00:39:01,288 --> 00:39:04,939
<font color="yellow">that you would take care of Dal-ho...</font>

572
00:39:06,140 --> 00:39:10,382
<font color="yellow">like he was your biological son.</font>

573
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:13,646
<font color="yellow">But right now...</font>

574
00:39:16,460 --> 00:39:17,992
<font color="yellow">I'm living in debt.</font>

575
00:39:18,648 --> 00:39:19,648
<font color="yellow">In debt.</font>

576
00:39:21,171 --> 00:39:22,171
<font color="yellow">Father,</font>

577
00:39:23,327 --> 00:39:26,425
<font color="yellow">I'm just your daughter-in-law by label.</font>

578
00:39:28,445 --> 00:39:31,249
<font color="yellow">I'm living a shabby life right now!</font>

579
00:39:32,905 --> 00:39:36,100
<font color="yellow">Why are you in debt?
