00:40:33,873 --> 00:40:34,873
<font color="yellow">Right?</font>

592
00:40:35,177 --> 00:40:37,815
<font color="yellow">Or else you wouldn't
be able to do this to us!</font>

593
00:40:38,521 --> 00:40:42,404
<font color="yellow">If you had really thought
