595
00:40:46,630 --> 00:40:47,903
<font color="yellow">Am I not right?</font>

596
00:40:48,638 --> 00:40:49,638
<font color="yellow">Chung-ja!</font>

597
00:40:50,341 --> 00:40:52,407
<font color="yellow">How dare you speak to him like that!</font>

598
00:40:52,755 --> 00:40:53,755
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

599
00:40:54,083 --> 00:40:55,528
<font color="yellow">Did I say something wrong?</font>

